# Neomorphism UI Redesign Implementation Plan

## Overview
Transform the ATS application to follow the **Neomorphism/Soft UI** design system as specified in [style_guild.md](file:///e:/TDC_App/ATS_TDSolutions-main/style_guild.md). This redesign will create a modern, tactile interface with soft shadows, rounded corners, and a light neutral color palette with orange accents.

## Key Design Changes

### Color Palette
- **Background**: Light beige (#f6f4ee) for the new login screen
- **General Background**: Light gray (#E5E5E5) for the rest of the app
- **Accent**: Orange (#FF9500) instead of blue
- **Shadows**: Neomorphic dual shadows (dark + light) for the app, soft minimalist shadows for the login screen
- **Typography**: Inter font family

### Visual Style
- **Shadows**: Multi-layered soft shadows for depth
- **Borders**: Minimal use, replaced with shadow-based separation
- **Radius**: Generous rounding (16px-32px)
- **Spacing**: More generous padding and margins

